{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTag","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Appearances","type":"heading","text":"Appearances"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have two appearances so as to highlight or not their content:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"emphasized"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a solid, high-contrast background. Used to draw strong attention to important"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"labels or categories. Emphasized tags stand out prominently against the interface and are ideal for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"primary or high-priority information."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"muted"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a subtle, light, or semi-transparent background. Used for secondary or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"less prominent information. Muted tags blend more with the background, providing a softer visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"emphasis compared to emphasized tags."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Status","type":"heading","text":"Status"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have seven status depending on the context of the information they represent. Each state is designed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to convey a specific meaning and ensure clarity in communication.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Neutral"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Default or inactive state. Used for standard labels, categories, or when no specific"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"status needs to be communicated."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accent"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Used to draw attention to new features, recommendations, or content suggestions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Invites users to explore and engage with new offerings, creating an exciting and engaging experience."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Positive"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Indicates success, confirmation, or a positive status. Commonly used to highlight"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"completed actions or approved items."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Warning"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Signals caution or a potentially risky situation. Used to draw attention to items"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"requiring user awareness or intervention."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Negative"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Represents errors, critical issues, or urgent attention needed. Used to highlight"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"problems or failed actions."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Info"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Conveys informational messages or supplementary details. Used for neutral, helpful,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or contextual information."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Disabled"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Shows that the tag is inactive and cannot be interacted with. Appears faded or greyed out. This is not"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"allowed when loader is activated."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Shape","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Shape"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags can have two shapes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Rounded"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with fully rounded corners, creating a pill-shaped appearance. Rounded"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tags offer a softer and more approachable look, suitable for most modern interfaces."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Square"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with sharp, square corners. Squared tags provide a more formal, structured, or"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"technical feel. They are often used in business contexts to label promotions, offers, or important notices."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Size","anchor":"Size","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two sizes:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Default"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": The standard tag size, suitable for most use cases and offering good readability.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Small","type":"text"}]},{"text":": A compact tag with reduced height and font size. Used when saving space is important or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when grouping elements visually.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Layout","level":2,"text":"Layout"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are four available layouts for tags:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text only"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that displays only text. Used for simple labels, categories, or keywords without additional visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"elements."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Bullet"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a small indicator (dot) alongside the text. Used to show status, presence, or activity"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"next to the label."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Icon"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that includes an icon before the text. Used to visually reinforce the meaning of the tag,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as status, type, or action."}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Loader","type":"text"}]},{"text":": A tag that combines a loading spinner (or progress indicator) with text. Used to indicate that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a process or action related to the tag is in progress.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","    \/\/ Or from a localizale and a bundle","    OUDSTag(LocalizedStringKey(\"label_wording\"), bundle: Bundle.module)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(leading: .bullet)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","    \/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","    \/\/ you can flip the icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","","    \/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","","    \/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","    OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-tag","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","level":3,"text":"Orange"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Orange-Compact","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading","text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Wireframe"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Version","style":"note"},{"name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.18.0","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note","type":"aside"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"platforms":[{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","unavailable":false,"name":"iOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"name":"macOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"16.0","unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"11.0","unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents7OUDSTagV","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"symbolKind":"struct","roleHeading":"Structure","title":"OUDSTag","modules":[{"name":"Components"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Status"],"anchor":"Structures","title":"Structures","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(_:tableName:bundle:status:appearance:shape:size:hasLoader:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(label:status:appearance:shape:size:hasLoader:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(loadingKey:tableName:bundle:shape:size:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(loadingLabel:shape:size:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/body"],"anchor":"Instance-Proper